{"tid":2421723,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"租中半山/跑馬地豪宅點睇？","createTime":"2021-02-24T16:42:37.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-01T02:32:42.000Z","uid":63048,"like":5,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"d192afe9a81a012303b91393e0230bc307cd6f12","tid":2421723,"uid":63048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T16:42:37.000Z","msg":"近排發現好多豪宅單位係發展商長期持有，只租不賣。而且裝修管理得非常好。唔洗十萬租就可以了享受幾千萬豪宅的享受。<br />\n<br />\n中半山似乎帝景園、曉峰閣、蘭心閣都不錯。<br />\n跑馬地就有曉籚同御峯。<br />\n<br />\n有無巴絲打住開可以分享吓？居住環境同物業管理有無邊座優勝啲？"},{"pid":"ecf7d08dfa8eaa2176f203577efcb571f47e9fc5","tid":2421723,"uid":236140,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T16:49:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 租豪宅冇得輸 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (我業主回報只有1釐多啲)<br />\n<br />\n不過我租緊九龍，四房雙套，頂級管理服務<br />\n<br />\n全天候暖水暖氣泳池，做GYM又唔使錢，邊度搵 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n等睇其他識享受嘅巴打介紹港島區 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"024fbfcbc6aa479e474dd2529787abacd0d80898","tid":2421723,"uid":11862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ecf7d08dfa8eaa2176f203577efcb571f47e9fc5","tid":2421723,"uid":236140,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T16:49:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 租豪宅冇得輸 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (我業主回報只有1釐多啲)<br />\n<br />\n不過我租緊九龍，四房雙套，頂級管理服務<br />\n<br />\n全天候暖水暖氣泳池，做GYM又唔使錢，邊度搵 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n等睇其他識享受嘅巴打介紹港島區 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T16:50:57.000Z","msg":"邊到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0654a043aa2d06f130020cf22681fbd65e44520","tid":2421723,"uid":63048,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid"